{"url": "https://www.ics.uci.edu/~kobsa/courses/ICS104/course-notes/incidents.htm", "content": "<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN\">\n<html><head><title>Incidents involving interface flaws</title>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=ISO-8859-1\"></head><body bgcolor=\"#ffffff\">\n<p><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\"><font size=\"7\"><b>A few \nincidents involving badly designed user interfaces</b></font></font></p><p>&nbsp;</p><blockquote> \n<p><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\">&#8226; A professor loses \nhalf an hour </font><a href=\"nsf-old.jpg\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"4\"><font face=\"Wingdings\" size=\"5\"><img style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 21px; height: 27px;\" alt=\"Thumb pointing down\" src=\"../../../graphics/thumb_down-small.png\"></font></font></font></font></a><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\"><a href=\"/courses/ICS205/course-notes/nsf-old.jpg\"></a></font></p><p><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\">&#8226; \nA professor and three staff lose two hours </font><a href=\"flawed-error-msg.htm\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"4\"><font face=\"Wingdings\" size=\"5\"><img style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 21px; height: 27px;\" alt=\"Thumb pointing down\" src=\"../../../graphics/thumb_down-small.png\"></font></font></font></font></a><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\"> \n  </font></p>\n  <p><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\">&#8226; Errors \nare made in presidential elections </font><a href=\"butterfly-ballot-booklet.png\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"4\"><font face=\"Wingdings\" size=\"5\"><img style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 21px; height: 27px;\" alt=\"Thumb pointing down\" src=\"../../../graphics/thumb_down-small.png\"></font></font></font></font></a><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\"> </font><a href=\"large.ballot.ap.jpg\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"4\"><font face=\"Wingdings\" size=\"5\"><img style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 21px; height: 27px;\" alt=\"Thumb pointing down\" src=\"../../../graphics/thumb_down-small.png\"></font></font></font></font></a><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\">&nbsp;</font></font><a href=\"butterfly-ballot-improved.png\"><big><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\" size=\"5\"><big><img style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 21px; height: 27px;\" alt=\"Error &quot;are you sure?&quot;\" src=\"../../../graphics/thumb_up.gif\"></big></font></big></a><a href=\"butterfly-ballot-improved.png\"><big><font face=\"Arial,Helvetica\" size=\"5\"><big> </big></font></big></a><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\"> \n  </font></p>\n\n  <p><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\">&#8226; An airliner \ngets shot down <a href=\"vincennes.gif\"><img src=\"../../../Graphics%20Templates/Diamonds/Di-red.gif\" alt=\"The picture shows U.S.S. Vincennes in open sea\" border=\"0\" height=\"11\" width=\"11\"></a>  </font><a href=\"http://catless.ncl.ac.uk/Risks/7.48.html#subj3\"><img style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 14px; height: 14px;\" alt=\"Link to more information on this incident\" src=\"../../../graphics/192px-Icon_External_Link.svg.png\"></a><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\"> \n  </font><a href=\"http://catless.ncl.ac.uk/Risks/7.67.html#subj6\"><img style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 14px; height: 14px;\" alt=\"Link to more information on this incident\" src=\"../../../graphics/192px-Icon_External_Link.svg.png\"></a><br>\n  <font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\"> \n  </font></p>\n  <p><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\">&#8226; A nuclear \npower plant gets out of control </font><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\"><a href=\"threemle.jpg\"><img src=\"../../../Graphics%20Templates/Diamonds/Di-red.gif\" alt=\"The image shows the Three-Mile Island nuclear power plant.\" border=\"0\" height=\"11\" width=\"11\"></a> </font><a href=\"large_denton.jpg\"><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\"><img style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 11px; height: 11px;\" src=\"../../../Graphics%20Templates/Diamonds/Di-red.gif\" alt=\"The image shows the control room of Three Miles Island, visited by Jimmy Carter during the accident.\"></font></a><font face=\"Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif\" size=\"6\"> \n</font><a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Three_Mile_Island_accident#Human_factors_.E2.80.93_confusion_over_valve_status\"><img style=\"border: 0px solid ; width: 14px; height: 14px;\" alt=\"Link to more information on this incident\" src=\"../../../graphics/192px-Icon_External_Link.svg.png\"></a></p>\n\n</blockquote>\n\n</body></html>", "encoding": "ascii"}